---
import '../styles/global.css'
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Privacy Policy | FlipSplit</title>
  <meta name="description" content="FlipSplit Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.flipsplit.com/privacy-policy" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.typekit.net/tbd3esf.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root { --brand-blue: #1a96e8; --brand-dark: #1E2A3A; --brand-body: #374151; }
    body { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; color: var(--brand-body); }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'sahar', 'Open Sans', sans-serif; color: var(--brand-dark); }
    .btn-primary { background: #1a96e8; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; transition: filter 0.15s ease; }
    .btn-primary:hover { filter: brightness(1.08); }
    .prose h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 900; color: #1E2A3A; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; }
    .prose p, .prose li { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.75; }
    .prose ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin: 0.75rem 0; }
    .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    a { cursor: pointer; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white antialiased">

  <!-- NAV -->
  <Nav />

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-b border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3" style="color:#1E2A3A;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Last updated: January 25, 2021</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose">

      <p>This privacy notice describes how FlipSplit LLC ("FlipSplit," "we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our website or services. FlipSplit operates in Southern California, serving Los Angeles, Orange County, San Diego, and the Inland Empire.</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Information you provide:</strong> We collect information you voluntarily provide when requesting an offer, registering an account, or contacting us — including your name, email address, phone number, and property address.</p>
      <p><strong>Automatically collected information:</strong> We automatically collect certain technical data including your IP address (or proxy server), device and application identification numbers, location, browser type, hardware model, internet service provider and/or mobile carrier, operating system, and system configuration information.</p>
      <p><strong>Location data:</strong> You may opt out of location tracking, though this may limit service functionality.</p>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>FlipSplit uses collected data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create and manage your account</li>
        <li>Deliver and improve our services</li>
        <li>Process and fulfill offer requests</li>
        <li>Send administrative and transactional communications</li>
        <li>Request feedback and post testimonials (with your consent)</li>
        <li>Protect against fraud and unauthorized access</li>
        <li>Send marketing communications (you may opt out at any time)</li>
        <li>Serve targeted advertising</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We may share your information in the following circumstances:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>With your consent</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        <li>With service providers under contract who assist in delivering our services</li>
        <li>During business transfers, mergers, or acquisitions</li>
        <li>With affiliated companies</li>
        <li>With business partners for joint promotions (with notice)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>FlipSplit LLC has not disclosed or sold any personal information to third parties for a business or commercial purpose in the preceding 12 months.</strong></p>

      <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve your experience on our site. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings or opt out of interest-based advertising at <a href="http://www.aboutads.info/choices/" style="color:#1a96e8;">www.aboutads.info/choices</a>.</p>

      <h2>5. Google Maps</h2>
      <p>Our site uses Google Maps Platform APIs to process location data. To revoke location consent, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@flipsplit.com" style="color:#1a96e8;">info@flipsplit.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by law. After that period, data is either deleted or anonymized.</p>

      <h2>7. Security</h2>
      <p>We implement organizational and technical security measures to protect your information. However, no electronic transmission or storage system can be guaranteed to be 100% secure. We encourage you to use strong passwords and keep your account credentials private.</p>

      <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>We do not knowingly collect data from or market to children under 18 years of age. If we discover that a minor has provided us with personal information, we will deactivate the account and delete the data promptly.</p>

      <h2>9. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request that inaccurate data be corrected</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request that your personal information be deleted</li>
        <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time using the link in any email, or by contacting us directly</li>
        <li><strong>Cookie control:</strong> Manage or remove cookies through your browser settings</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not currently respond to Do-Not-Track (DNT) browser signals, as no uniform standard has been finalized.</p>

      <h2>10. California Resident Rights (CCPA)</h2>
      <p>If you are a California resident, you have additional rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), including the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Know what personal information is collected, used, shared, or sold</li>
        <li>Delete personal information held by us</li>
        <li>Opt out of the sale of personal information</li>
        <li>Non-discrimination for exercising your CCPA rights</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We collect the following category of personal information: <strong>Category B</strong> — name, contact information, and property details. We do not collect biometric data, geolocation, commercial transaction data, or other sensitive categories.</p>
      <p>To submit a CCPA request, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@flipsplit.com" style="color:#1a96e8;">info@flipsplit.com</a>. We will verify your identity and respond within 30 days.</p>

      <h2>11. Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated by updating the date at the top of this page or by direct notification. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>

      <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions or wish to exercise any of your privacy rights, contact us at:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@flipsplit.com" style="color:#1a96e8;">info@flipsplit.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:18006617489" style="color:#1a96e8;">1-800-661-7489</a></li>
        <li><strong>Mail:</strong> FlipSplit LLC, 1590 S Coast Hwy #16, Laguna Beach, CA 92651</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <a href="/"><img src="/wordmark.png" alt="FlipSplit" class="h-8" /></a>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <a href="/how-it-works" class="hover:text-[#1E2A3A] transition-colors">How It Works</a>
        <a href="/reviews" class="hover:text-[#1E2A3A] transition-colors">Reviews</a>
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-[#1E2A3A] transition-colors">About</a>
        <a href="/faq" class="hover:text-[#1E2A3A] transition-colors">FAQ</a>
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="font-semibold" style="color:#1E2A3A;">Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">© 2026 FlipSplit. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
